        ("What does CEREC stand for?",
         "Chairside Economical Restoration of Esthetic Ceramic — a digital system that designs and mills custom ceramic crowns, onlays, inlays, and veneers right in our office. The 'chairside' part is the key benefit: no temporary crowns, no second visit, no lab wait."),
